---
// Hero component for overseas bank account closure service
---

<section class="p-6 sm:p-12" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Service">
  <div
    class="reveal-from-left relative h-[calc(100vh-3rem)] rounded-2xl bg-[url(../assets/images/hero_sm.jpg)] bg-cover bg-no-repeat sm:h-[calc(100vh-6rem)] sm:bg-[url(../assets/images/hero.jpg)]"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-6 sm:justify-start sm:pl-12"
    >
      <div class="max-w-4xl text-center sm:text-left">
        <h2
          class="slide-in-left mb-4 text-3xl/tight font-black text-white opacity-0 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
          itemprop="name"
        >
          海外口座、<br />放置していませんか？
        </h2>
        <h3
          class="slide-in-left text-sm font-semibold text-white opacity-0 delay-200 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
        >
          <strong>
            現地渡航不要！英語力不要！面倒な解約手続きをプロが完全サポート
          </strong>
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul
      class="fade-in-up absolute bottom-20 left-6 space-y-2 opacity-0 delay-800 sm:left-12"
    >
      <li class="font-bold text-white drop-shadow-lg">
        <strong>現地に行かずに、閉じられます！</strong>
      </li>
      <li class="font-bold text-white drop-shadow-lg">
        <strong>もちろん口座内の預金はご指定の銀行口座に送金可能！</strong>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p
      class="fade-in-up absolute bottom-10 left-6 text-sm text-white opacity-0 drop-shadow-lg delay-1000 sm:left-12"
    >
      口座凍結・州政府移管・相続手続き…
      <br />
      複雑な海外口座の問題を、実績多数の専門チームが解決します。
    </p>

    <!-- Floating info card -->
    <div
      class="fade-in-up absolute top-20 right-6 rounded-lg bg-white/90 p-4 opacity-0 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm transition-transform delay-600 duration-300 hover:scale-105 sm:top-32 sm:right-20"
    >
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">
        実績多数の専門チームが
      </div>
      <div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">
        あなたの海外口座を<br />スッキリ解決
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
